OL,3,CEx-firefighter jailed after paying
OL,4,Cchildren to send explicit images
OL,6,FA former firefighter from Derbyshire
OL,7,Fhas been jailed after paying children
OL,8,Fto send him explicit images online.
OL,10,FRobert Stevenson, 31, used his social
OL,11,Fmedia sites to message young girls,
OL,12,Foffering them money to send naked
OL,13,Fpictures.
OL,15,FHe sent a photo of himself in uniform
OL,16,Fto one of his victims, claiming to be
OL,17,F19.
