OL,6,FOne of Stevenson's victims, who is a
OL,7,F15-year-old girl, told Derbyshire
OL,8,FPolice he had threatened to post an
OL,9,Fexplicit picture of her online.
OL,11,FHe had spoken to the girl through
OL,12,Fdirect messages on Instagram, asking
OL,13,Fher if she wanted to make one hundred
OL,14,Fpounds.
OL,16,FThey then messaged on Snapchat, with
OL,17,FStevenson telling her he was also 17,
OL,18,Fafter she told him her age.
OL,20,FStevenson was arrested and his devices
OL,21,Fwere seized.
